settings.question: Does Craftmix taste as good as liquid mixers?

settings.answer: No one likes a chalky cocktail! Sugar helps our flavors dissolve better and also gives your cocktail a more balanced taste and texture! Donâ€™t worry, itâ€™s natural sugar and only about 1/8th of what the standard cocktail mix uses!

settings.title: What is Craftmix?
settings.answer: Craftmix is an all natural cocktail mix that comes in a dry blend! We make cocktails that are delicious, convenient, and guilt-free! Our better-for-you cocktail mixes have only 25 calories and 5g of sugar per drink! Plus Craftmix comes in small packets that way you can now enjoy happy hour anywhere!

settings.title: How do I make a Craftmix cocktail?
settings.answer:
-Start with 1 shot of booze (1.5oz)
-Add 2 shots of sparkling or still water (3oz)
-Mix in one Craftmix packet thoroughly
-Serve over ice and enjoy :)

settings.title: Why not use a liquid cocktail mix?
settings.answer: Who wants to show up to the party all sweaty? Definitely not Craftmix! Ditch those heavy glass bottles of neon-colored mystery liquid, and slip a few Craftmix packets into your pocket or purse and youâ€™re good to go!

settings.title: Does Craftmix taste as good as liquid mixers?

settings.answer: Did you know the average liquid cocktail mix has over 150 calories and 30 grams of sugar? That's because liquid cocktail mixes typically use syrups that are high in sugar and other artificial chemicals! Craftmix avoids that junk by dehydrating real fruit and concentrating it into our delicious blends!

settings.title: Why does Craftmix have a small amount of sugar?
settings.answer: No one likes a chalky cocktail! Sugar helps our flavors dissolve better and also gives your cocktail a more balanced, taste and texture! Donâ€™t worry, itâ€™s natural sugar and only about 1/8thÂ of what the standard cocktail mix uses!

settings.title: How many calories and how much sugar does Craftmix have?

settings.title: Can I enjoy Craftmix without alcohol?

settings.title: Where should I use Craftmix?
settings.answer: The possibilities are endless! Craftmix is great for tailgates, sports venues, camping, planes, festivals, concerts, picnics, and even rocket ships to the moon!

settings.title: What tastes best with Craftmix?
settings.answer: We recommend using your 1.5oz of favorite liquor and 3oz of sparkling water or club soda to give your cocktail a little bit of zing! Enjoy those bubbles!

settings.title: How do you formulate your blends?
settings.answer: We canâ€™t tell you our secret formula! But what we can tell you is we have a special method of dehydrating fruit flavors to taste fresh and juicy! Straight from the fruit, right to your palate!
